<title>ʿạyzynk ạ̹nt wḥdk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ʿạyzynk ạ̹nt wḥdk .. yạ ṣạḥb ạlwʿwd
 ʿạyzynk ạ̹nt wḥdk .. bkẖyrk lynạ tjwd)2
 ạlqrạr- (wttmjd fy wsṭynạ .. wtfyḍ brwḥk fynạ)2
 (yạ yswʿ .. yạ yswʿ .. yạ yswʿ)2
